714214f-a.title: Manhattan: 67th Street (West) - Central Park West
714214f-a.text:
(1)
28 West 67th Street, south side, west of Central Park West.
This is a two-story frame building.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 515.
(2)
The same, five years earlier.
November 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
